reviewText: Simply a FLAWLESS performance of these pieces.  Must have.

Excellent. I purchased the DVD primarily after seeing the clip of "La Catedral" on youtube. I was not disappointed. The other pieces are also rendered masterfully. I enjoyed the bit of history that Mr. Azabagic provides  on the composers and the pieces. I highly recommend this DVD to music aficionados.

Denis Azabagic performs brilliantly in this DVD.  A true master of the classical guitar, his performance of Agustin Barrios Mangore's La Catedral is truly amazing.  A must have DVD for the classical guitar student or enthusiast.
